services.title: Workday - Software Developer in Test
services.description: I led backend and frontend testing efforts, developed a performance-enhancing toolkit, and streamlined test processes through migration. These contributions have improved software quality, testing efficiency, and end-user satisfaction.

services.title: SAP - Software Developer
services.description: I enhanced key features of SAP Analytics Cloud, leading to significant performance improvements and increased client satisfaction. Proactive strategies, including Remote Debugging and Ask Mode Testing, enabled swift issue resolution, enhancing customer satisfaction. I achieved top-ranking test coverage of over 97% among ten teams through the development of automation tests and CI/CD pipelines in Jasmine and Jenkins. Collaboration with cross-functional teams and the use of online tools streamlined our agile software development workflow.
